<div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: brown"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Portal_Buddhism_DYK_11&action=edit.php.html"><span style="color: brown">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>
<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:brown;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Did_you_know...">Did you know...</span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid sandybrown; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: ivory;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<div style="float:right;margin-left:0.5em;">
<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Itigelov.jpg" class="image" title="Dashi-Dorzho Itigelov"><img alt="Dashi-Dorzho Itigelov" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/Itigelov.jpg/82px-Itigelov.jpg" width="82" height="100" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/Itigelov.jpg/123px-Itigelov.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/Itigelov.jpg/163px-Itigelov.jpg 2x" /></a></p>
</div>
<ul>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">...that the body of <b><a href="Dashi-Dorzho_Itigelov" title="Dashi-Dorzho Itigelov" class="mw-redirect">Dashi-Dorzho Itigelov</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i>, who led the <a href="Buddhism_in_Russia" title="Buddhism in Russia">Russian Buddhists</a> from <a href="1911" title="1911">1911</a> until his death in <a href="1927" title="1927">1927</a>, is said to exhibit <a href="Incorruptibility" title="Incorruptibility">no signs of physical decay</a>?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">...that <a href="Zen" title="Zen">Zen</a> <a href="Buddhism" title="Buddhism">Buddhist</a> scholar <b><a href="Philip_Yampolsky" title="Philip Yampolsky">Philip Yampolsky</a></b> was the grandson of <a href="Frank_Boas" title="Frank Boas" class="mw-redirect">Frank Boas</a>, the founder of <a href="Columbia_University" title="Columbia University">Columbia University</a>'s <a href="Anthropology" title="Anthropology">anthropology</a> department?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">...that <a href="Firearms" title="Firearms" class="mw-redirect">arms</a>, <a href="Munitions" title="Munitions" class="mw-redirect">munitions</a>, and <a href="Vietcong" title="Vietcong" class="mw-redirect">Vietcong</a> documents were planted prior to <b><a href="Xa_Loi_Pagoda_raids" title="Xa Loi Pagoda raids" class="mw-redirect">raids on South Vietnam's Buddhist pagodas</a></b> as a pretext to crush protests over religious discrimination?
<table class="noprint" width="100%" border="0" style="padding: 0; margin: 0; background-color:transparent">
<tr>
<td>
<div style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:0px;"><b><a href="DYK/index.html" title="Portal:Buddhism/DYK">...Archive/Nominations</a></b></div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="text-align:right;margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:0px;">
<p><b><a href="Wikipedia_Recent_additions" title="Wikipedia:Recent additions">More...</a></b></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
